# Code Review Checklist

- [ ] Layer boundaries respected (n8n / backend / playwright / LLM)
- [ ] No `any`; strict TypeScript
- [ ] Controllers thin; logic in use cases; Prisma only in repositories
- [ ] Idempotent where retries can fire
- [ ] Env-based config; no secrets in code
- [ ] Structured logging present
- [ ] Errors handled and observable
- [ ] Playwright: Locator API, no fixed waits, failure screenshots
- [ ] Tests or stubs for new use cases when feasible
- [ ] Migrations included for schema changes
